trans-unit.source: Describes a two-dimensional rectangle.
trans-unit.target: 描述二維矩形。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> class, and creates a rectangle with zero area.
trans-unit.target: 建立 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 類別的新執行個體，並建立具有零值區域的矩形。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> structure with the rectangle's dimensions.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> 結構，具有矩形的維度。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> class and specifies its dimensions.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 類別的新執行個體並指定其維度。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> structure with the rectangle's dimensions.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> 結構，具有矩形的維度。

trans-unit.source: The radius of the rounded corner where it connects with the upper and lower edges of the rectangle.
trans-unit.target: 圓角與矩形的下邊緣和下邊緣連接的半徑。

trans-unit.source: The radius of the rounded corner where it connects with the left and right edges of the rectangle.
trans-unit.target: 圓角與矩形的左邊緣和右邊緣連接的半徑。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> structure with the rectangle's dimensions.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> 結構，具有矩形的維度。

trans-unit.source: The radius of the rounded corner where it connects with the upper and lower edges of the rectangle.
trans-unit.target: 圓角與矩形的下邊緣和下邊緣連接的半徑。

trans-unit.source: The radius of the rounded corner where it connects with the left and right edges of the rectangle.
trans-unit.target: 圓角與矩形的左邊緣和右邊緣連接的半徑。

trans-unit.source: The transformation to apply to the geometry.
trans-unit.target: 套用至幾何的轉換。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> that specifies the bounding box of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" />.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" />，其指定 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 的週框方塊。

trans-unit.source: This method does not take any pens into account.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法不會將任何畫筆納入考量。

trans-unit.source: The bounding box of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 的週框方塊。

trans-unit.source: If animations are present, the base values of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry> object are used to calculate the bounding box.
trans-unit.target: 如果動畫會呈現，基底值<xref:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry>物件用來計算週框方塊。

trans-unit.source: Creates a modifiable clone of this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" />, making deep copies of this object's values.
trans-unit.target: 建立這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 的可修改複製品，深層複製這個物件的值。

trans-unit.source: When copying dependency properties, this method copies resource references and data bindings (but they might no longer resolve) but not animations or their current values.
trans-unit.target: 當複製相依性屬性時，這個方法會複製資源參考和資料繫結 (但可能無法再解析)，但不會複製動畫或它們目前的值。

trans-unit.source: A modifiable clone of the current object.
trans-unit.target: 目前物件的可修改複本。

trans-unit.source: The cloned object's <see cref="P:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen" /> property will be <see langword="false" /> even if the source's <see cref="P:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen" /> property was <see langword="true." />
trans-unit.target: 即使來源的 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen" /> 屬性為 <see langword="true." />，複製物件的 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen" /> 屬性將仍為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: This method is used to produce modifiable copies of frozen <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> objects (or any <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> object).
trans-unit.target: 這個方法用來產生的可修改複本凍結<xref:System.Windows.Freezable>物件 (或任何<xref:System.Windows.Freezable>物件)。

trans-unit.source: For convenience, this method shadows the inherited version with a strongly typed implementation.
trans-unit.target: 為了方便起見，這個方法會遮蔽強型別實作繼承的版本。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.Clone%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱<xref:System.Windows.Freezable.Clone%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>。

trans-unit.source: Creates a modifiable clone of this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> object, making deep copies of this object's current values.
trans-unit.target: 建立這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 物件的可修改複製品，製作這個物件目前值的深層複本。

trans-unit.source: Resource references, data bindings, and animations are not copied, but their current values are.
trans-unit.target: 不會複製資源參考、資料繫結和動畫，但是會複製其目前值。

trans-unit.source: A modifiable clone of the current object.
trans-unit.target: 目前物件的可修改複本。

trans-unit.source: The cloned object's <see cref="P:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen" /> property will be <see langword="false" /> even if the source's <see cref="P:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen" /> property was <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 即使來源的 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen" /> 屬性為 <see langword="false" />，複製物件的 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen" /> 屬性將仍為 <see langword="true" />。

trans-unit.source: This method is used to produce modifiable copies of frozen <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> objects (or any <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> object).
trans-unit.target: 這個方法用來產生的可修改複本凍結<xref:System.Windows.Freezable>物件 (或任何<xref:System.Windows.Freezable>物件)。

trans-unit.source: For convenience, this method shadows the inherited version with a strongly typed implementation.
trans-unit.target: 為了方便起見，這個方法會遮蔽強型別實作繼承的版本。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.CloneCurrentValue%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱<xref:System.Windows.Freezable.CloneCurrentValue%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>。

trans-unit.source: The computational tolerance of error.
trans-unit.target: 容許的計算誤差。

trans-unit.source: Specifies how the error tolerance will be interpreted.
trans-unit.target: 指定容許誤差的解譯方式。

trans-unit.source: Gets the area of the filled region of this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 取得這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 物件的填滿區域。

trans-unit.source: The area of the filled region of this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 物件的填滿區域。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> object is empty.
trans-unit.target: 判斷這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 物件是否空白。

trans-unit.source: **true** if this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> is empty; otherwise, **false**.
trans-unit.target: 若這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 是空的則為 **true**否則為 **false**。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> object may have curved segments.
trans-unit.target: 判斷這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 物件是否可以具有弧形片段。

trans-unit.source: **true** if this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> object may have curved segments; otherwise, **false**.
trans-unit.target: 若這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry" /> 物件可以具有弧形片段，則為 **true**；否則為 **false**。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the x-radius of the ellipse use to round the corners of the rectangle.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定將矩形變成圓角時，所用橢圓形的 X 半徑。

trans-unit.source: A value greater than or equal to zero and less than or equal to half the rectangle's width that describes the x-radius of the ellipse use to round the corners of the rectangle.
trans-unit.target: 大於或等於零且小於或等於矩形寬度一半的值，這個值描述將矩形變成圓角時，所用橢圓形的 X 半徑。

trans-unit.source: Values greater than half the rectangle's width are treated as though equal to half the rectangle's width.
trans-unit.target: 大於矩形寬度一半的值會視為等於矩形寬度的一半。

trans-unit.source: Negative values are treated as positive values.
trans-unit.target: 負值會視為正值。

trans-unit.source: The default is <c>0.0</c>.
trans-unit.target: 預設值是<c>0.0</c>。

trans-unit.source: For the rectangle to have rounded corners, both the <xref:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry.RadiusX%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry.RadiusY%2A> properties must be non-zero.
trans-unit.target: 為具有圓角矩形同時<xref:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry.RadiusX%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry.RadiusY%2A>屬性必須是非零。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the y-radius of the ellipse use to round the corners of the rectangle.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定橢圓形的 Y 軸半徑，用來決定矩形的圓角程度。

trans-unit.source: A value greater than or equal to zero and less than or equal to half the rectangle's width that describes the y-radius of the ellipse use to round the corners of the rectangle.
trans-unit.target: 大於或等於零且小於或等於矩形寬度一半的值，這個值描述將矩形變成圓角時，所用橢圓形的 Y 半徑。

trans-unit.source: Values greater than half the rectangle's width are treated as though equal to half the rectangle's width.
trans-unit.target: 大於矩形寬度一半的值會視為等於矩形寬度的一半。

trans-unit.source: Negative values are treated as positive values.
trans-unit.target: 負值會視為正值。

trans-unit.source: The default is <c>0.0</c>.
trans-unit.target: 預設值是<c>0.0</c>。

trans-unit.source: For the rectangle to have rounded corners, both the <xref:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry.RadiusX%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry.RadiusY%2A> properties must be non-zero.
trans-unit.target: 為具有圓角矩形同時<xref:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry.RadiusX%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Media.RectangleGeometry.RadiusY%2A>屬性必須是非零。
